CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

August 1, 2008

[Cite as 08/01/2008 Case Announcements, 2008-Ohio-3825.]

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2008-1150. Van Beusecum v. Continental Builders, Inc.

Delaware App. No. 06CAE12-0095, 2008-Ohio-2141. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal and claimed appeal of right. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
